{"tid":2145521,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"劉兆佳料中央對港更強硬　馮智政：美對華政策不會大變","createTime":"2020-08-08T05:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T10:22:37.000Z","uid":278587,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"0db219059d46ee907582d6f6bfac28b9ad1a9523","tid":2145521,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T05:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1542554_2_20200808130728.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1542554_2_20200808130728.jpg&h=0c3531fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全國港澳研究會副會長劉兆佳認為，制裁名單是意料之內，預料中方很快會推出反制措施，對港問題的態度亦會更強硬。<br />\n<br />\n時事評論員馮智政說，美國的對華政策是民主、共和兩黨的共識，即使美國總統換人，對華政策亦不會大逆轉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542554-20200808.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542554-20200808.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDBD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=ea7505b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542554-20200808.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8bc58c86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542554-20200808.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"2f0b5885ab49fd43aef55afdd784b6999f8b2caf","tid":2145521,"uid":290883,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T05:58:22.000Z","msg":"as long as Xi is still there，"},{"pid":"5d9503786ea0945a49ee11d6b264ba391dab06bf","tid":2145521,"uid":83713,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T05:58:31.000Z","msg":"佳叔對上一次估中係幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cfccd18f785e9e8bddc098b0c2d525db7fefa63","tid":2145521,"uid":134323,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T05:59:59.000Z","msg":"劉兆佳終極 9up 師"},{"pid":"eb8b859032c482304a902a11